tasks.task: Apply RimGuard to tractor tires for safety and stability.
subtasks: Ensure tractor is off and cool.
Measure 10.7 pounds per gallon of RimGuard.
Pour RimGuard into rear tires of Summit TX25 equipped with RimGuard.
Check front-end loader stability after application.
Monitor and maintain RimGuard levels as needed.

tasks.task: Search for RimGuard dealer if not on Summit TX25.
subtasks: Confirm dealership locations from provided list.
Enter location to find nearest dealer.
Note dealer contact information for future reference.
Prepare vehicle for travel to selected dealership.
